Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:08.60,灰英字,,0,0,0,,One of the exciting things about a large language model is you could use it to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:12.68,灰英字,,0,0,0,,build a custom chatbot with only a modest amount of effort
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:17.66,灰英字,,0,0,0,,ChatGPT, the web interface is a way for you to have a conversational interface
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:20.50,灰英字,,0,0,0,,a conversation via a large language model
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:23.12,灰英字,,0,0,0,,But one of the cool things is you can also use
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:25.68,灰英字,,0,0,0,,a large language model to build your custom chatbot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:28.92,灰英字,,0,0,0,,to maybe play the role of an AI customer service agent or
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:31.48,灰英字,,0,0,0,,an AI order taker for restaurants
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:34.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And in this video, you learn how to do that for yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:37.08,灰英字,,0,0,0,,I'm going to describe the components of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:39.96,灰英字,,0,0,0,,the OpenAI chat completions format in more detail
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.96,0:00:42.54,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and then you're going to build a chatbot yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:44.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So let's get into it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:49.00,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So first, we'll set up the OpenAI Python package as usual
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:53.38,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So chat models like ChatGPT are actually trained to take a series of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:00:57.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,messages as input and return a model generated message as output
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:59.96,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And so although the chat format is designed to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.96,0:01:02.32,灰英字,,0,0,0,,make multi-turn conversations like this easy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:06.00,灰英字,,0,0,0,,we've kind of seen through the previous videos that it's also just as
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:09.56,灰英字,,0,0,0,,useful for single-turn tasks without any conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:14.20,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And so next, we're going to kind of define two helper functions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.20,0:01:17.08,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So this is the one that we've been using throughout all the videos
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.08,0:01:20.36,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and it's the get_completion function
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:22.08,灰英字,,0,0,0,,But if you kind of look at it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.08,0:01:25.04,灰英字,,0,0,0,,we give a prompt, but then kind of inside the function
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:29.32,灰英字,,0,0,0,,what we're actually doing is putting this prompt into what looks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.32,0:01:32.16,灰英字,,0,0,0,,what looks like some kind of user message
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:37.20,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And this is because the ChatGPT model is a chat model
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:40.20,灰英字,,0,0,0,,which means it's trained to take a series of messages as input
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:44.00,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and then return model generated messages output
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:45.88,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So the user message is kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:49.32,灰英字,,0,0,0,,the input and then the assistant message is the output
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:51.32,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So in this video
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:53.76,灰英字,,0,0,0,,we're going to actually use a different helper function
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:55.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And instead of kind of putting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:58.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,a single prompt as input and getting a single completion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:01.68,灰英字,,0,0,0,,we're going to pass in a list of messages
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:05.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And these messages can be kind of from a variety of different roles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:07.16,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So I'll describe those
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:10.04,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So here's an example of a list of messages
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:12.04,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And so the first message is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:15.20,灰英字,,0,0,0,,a system message which kind of gives an overall instruction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:16.36,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And then after this message
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:20.04,灰英字,,0,0,0,,we have kind of turns between the user and the assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:21.92,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And this is kind of continue to go on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:24.80,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And if you've ever used ChatGPT, the web interface
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:27.68,灰英字,,0,0,0,,then your messages are the user messages
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:30.88,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and then ChatGPT's messages are the assistant messages
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:33.44,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So the system message helps to kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:35.80,灰英字,,0,0,0,,set the behavior and persona of the assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.92,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and it acts as kind of a high-level instruction for the conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:40.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So you can kind of think of it as whispering in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:42.44,灰英字,,0,0,0,,the assistant's ear and kind of guiding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:46.32,灰英字,,0,0,0,,its responses without the user being aware of the system message
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:47.96,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So as the user
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:49.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,if you've ever used ChatGPT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:52.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,you probably don't know what's in ChatGPT's system message
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:55.36,灰英字,,0,0,0,,The benefit of the system message is that it provides you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.24,灰英字,,0,0,0,,the developer, with a way to kind of frame
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:59.12,灰英字,,0,0,0,,the conversation without making
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:01.32,灰英字,,0,0,0,,the request itself part of the conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:04.88,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So you can kind of guide the assistant and kind of whisper in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:09.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,its ear and guide its responses without making the user aware
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:15.44,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So now let's try to use these messages in a conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:19.16,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So we'll use our new helper function to get
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:21.72,灰英字,,0,0,0,,the completion from the messages
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:27.20,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and we're also using a higher temperature
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So the system message says
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:31.44,灰英字,,0,0,0,,you are an assistant that speaks like Shakespeare
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.16,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So this is us kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:35.96,灰英字,,0,0,0,,describing to the assistant how it should behave
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.68,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and then the first user message is, tell me a joke
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:41.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,The next is, why did the chicken cross the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:45.52,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Then the final user message is, I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:49.88,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So if we run this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:55.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,the response is to get to the other side. Let's try again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:57.92,灰英字,,0,0,0,,To get to the other side
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.24,灰英字,,0,0,0,,fair sir or madam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:02.04,灰英字,,0,0,0,,it is an old and classic that never fails
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:05.12,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So that's our Shakespearean response
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.96,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Let's actually try one more thing because I want to make
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:11.52,灰英字,,0,0,0,,it even clearer that this is the assistant message
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:19.36,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So here let's just go and print the entire message response
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:36.24,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So just to make this even clearer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:41.16,灰英字,,0,0,0,,this response is an assistant message
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:45.68,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So the role is assistant and then the content is the message itself
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.00,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So that's what's happening in this helper function
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:51.88,灰英字,,0,0,0,,We're just passing out the content of the message
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:07.96,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So now let's do another example
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:09.84,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So here our messages are
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:13.16,灰英字,,0,0,0,,the system message is you're a friendly chatbot
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:14.56,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and the first user message is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:16.12,灰英字,,0,0,0,,hi, my name is Isa
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:20.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,We want to get the first user message
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:22.08,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So let's execute this
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:24.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,the first assistant message
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:26.88,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So the first message is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:28.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,hello Isa, it's nice to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:30.76,灰英字,,0,0,0,,How can I assist you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.76,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Now let's try another example
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:43.72,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So here our messages are system message
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:45.12,灰英字,,0,0,0,,you're a friendly chatbot
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:47.08,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and the first user message is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:53.88,灰英字,,0,0,0,,yes, can you remind me what is my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:56.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Let's get the response
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:06:01.44,灰英字,,0,0,0,,As you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:05.80,灰英字,,0,0,0,,the model doesn't actually know my name
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:10.68,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So each conversation with a language model is a standalone interaction
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:13.20,灰英字,,0,0,0,,which means that you must provide all relevant messages
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:16.12,灰英字,,0,0,0,,for the model to draw from in the current conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:18.56,灰英字,,0,0,0,,If you want the model to draw from or
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:21.24,灰英字,,0,0,0,,quote unquote, remember earlier parts of a conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:24.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,you must provide the earlier exchanges in the input to the model
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:26.96,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So we'll refer to this as context
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:30.24,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So let's try this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:39.00,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So now we've given the context that the model needs
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.60,灰英字,,0,0,0,,which is my name in the previous messages
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:43.16,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and we'll ask the same question
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:45.64,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So we'll ask what my name is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:50.32,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and the model is able to respond because it has all of the context it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:55.52,灰英字,,0,0,0,,needs in this list of messages that we input to it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:58.76,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So now you're going to build your own chatbot
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:02.04,灰英字,,0,0,0,,This chatbot is going to be called orderbot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:05.52,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and we're going to automate the collection of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:09.48,灰英字,,0,0,0,,user prompts and assistant responses in order to build this orderbot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:12.20,灰英字,,0,0,0,,It's going to take orders at a pizza restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:16.04,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So first, we're going to define this helper function
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:19.04,灰英字,,0,0,0,,What this is doing is it's going to collect
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:24.84,灰英字,,0,0,0,,our user messages so we can avoid typing them in by hand in the way that we did above
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:29.76,灰英字,,0,0,0,,This is going to collect prompts from a user interface that we'll build below
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.80,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and then append it to a list called context
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:36.28,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and then it will call the model with that context every time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:39.32,灰英字,,0,0,0,,The model response is then also added to the context
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:43.56,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So the model message is added to the context
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.16,灰英字,,0,0,0,,the user message is added to the context
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:47.88,灰英字,,0,0,0,,so on, so it just grows longer and longer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:52.68,灰英字,,0,0,0,,This way, the model has the information it needs to determine what to do next
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:58.60,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So now we'll set up and run this UI to display the orderbot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:00.36,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So here's the context
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:04.20,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and it contains the system message that contains the menu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:08.16,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Note that every time we call the language model
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:13.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,we're going to use the same context and the context is building up over time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:19.04,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Then let's execute this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:25.76,灰英字,,0,0,0,,I'm going to say, hi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:29.44,灰英字,,0,0,0,,I would like to order a pizza
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:35.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,The assistant says, great
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:36.88,灰英字,,0,0,0,,what pizza would you like to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:40.52,灰英字,,0,0,0,,We have pepperoni, cheese, and eggplant pizza
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:44.68,灰英字,,0,0,0,,How much are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:56.88,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Great. Okay, we have the prices
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:09:12.00,灰英字,,0,0,0,,I think I'm feeling a medium eggplant pizza. So as you can imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:14.00,灰英字,,0,0,0,,we could continue this conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:17.72,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Let's look at what we've put in the system message
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:20.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So you are orderbot
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:23.28,灰英字,,0,0,0,,an automated service to collect orders for a pizza restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:24.60,灰英字,,0,0,0,,You first greet the customer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:27.80,灰英字,,0,0,0,,then collect the order and then ask if it's a pickup or delivery
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.48,灰英字,,0,0,0,,You wait to collect the entire order
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:31.68,灰英字,,0,0,0,,then summarize it and check for a final time
