Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.40,灰英字,,0,0,0,,If it's a delivery, you can ask for an address
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:38.04,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Finally, you collect the payment
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:40.24,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Make sure to clarify all options, extras
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:43.12,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and sizes to uniquely identify the item from the menu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.92,灰英字,,0,0,0,,You respond in a short
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:46.84,灰英字,,0,0,0,,very conversational, friendly style
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:50.88,灰英字,,0,0,0,,The menu includes, and then here we have the menu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:54.20,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So let's go back to our conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:58.72,灰英字,,0,0,0,,And let's see if the assistant kind of has been following the instructions
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.72,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Okay, great. The assistant asks if we want any toppings
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:05.76,灰英字,,0,0,0,,which we kind of specified in the system message
